steps.html_instructions: Take exit 243 on the left for Mounds Blvd
Keep left at the fork to continue on I-35E S, follow signs for Interstate 35E S

I-35E S turns slightly right and becomes I-35 S
Entering Iowa
Take the I-35 S/I-80 exit toward Kansas City/Council Bluffs/Davenport
Keep left at the fork to continue on Exit 137A, follow signs for I-80 E/Davenport
Take exit 141 for US-65 S toward Altoona/Des Moines
Take exit 79 for IA-163/E University Ave toward Pleasant Hill

Turn left onto IA-163 E/E University Ave
Continue to follow IA-163 E
Take the ramp to US-34 W/US-63 S
Slight left to stay on US-34 W/US-63 S
At the traffic circle, take the 2nd exit onto US-63 S
Merge onto US-54 W/US-63 S via the ramp to Jefferson City
